interview: बाबा छोटा सा एक अपना परिचय देदेंगे, क्या नाम है, कहाँ से belong करते हैं, क्या काम करते हैं?
----
Interview: Baba, will you introduce yourself a little, what is your name, where do you belong from, what work do you do?

5
00:00:19,416 --> 00:00:21,625
baba: जी हमारा नाम प्रदीप पुरी है
----
baba: Yes, my name is Pradeep Puri.

6
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:25,333
हम 14 वर्ष से नागा साधु हैं
----
We have been Naga Sadhus for 14 years

7
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:31,416
और हमारा जन्म हरयाणा, रोहतक district में हुआ है
----
And I was born in Haryana, Rohtak district

8
00:00:32,666 --> 00:00:33,958
interview: एक सेकंड रुको
----
interview: wait a second

9
00:00:35,416 --> 00:00:50,208
phone rang and the interviewer speaks about some issue with something
----
phone rang and the interviewer speaks about some issue with something

